    Customizable Options

    Unlock endless possibilities with our customizable options. Practically the whole steering wheel can be customized, from top to bottom.

    Here's a list of customizable options available (But not limited to):

     

    • Steering Wheel Type

    Choose from a variety of steering wheel types tailored to your driving needs and style preferences. Whether you prefer a mix of materials, fully Alcantara, fully leather or fully carbon, we have the perfect fit for you.

     

    • Steering Wheel Shape

    Select the shape that best suits your driving style. Options range from traditional round shapes to F1 style designs, each offering unique ergonomic and aesthetic benefits.

     

    • Carbon Type & Finishing

    Customize the carbon fibre style of your steering wheel with various types and finishes. Opt the usual 3K twill weave to forged infused carbon, finished either in gloss or matte. You will have no issue selecting the carbon type of your liking.

     

    • Side Grip Material & Colour

    Enhance your grip and comfort with premium side grip materials. Choose from leather or Alcantara, to a colour choice that suits your personal taste.

     

    • Stitching Type & Colour

    Add a personal touch with custom stitching style. Select your preferred stitching type and colour to complement the overall design of your steering wheel that matches your vehicles interior/exterior - or the opposite, to stand out.

     

    • Apex Line & Colour

    Include an apex line for a sporty, racing-inspired look, or just exclude if that's not your thing. Customize the color to match or contrast with your steering wheel for a striking look.

     

    • LED

    These can provide useful information at a glance, enhancing both functionality and aesthetics. For more information about our racing style LEDs, refer to the "LED functions" tab.

     

    • Paddle Shifts

    Choose from various paddle shift types, including magnetic paddle shifts and carbon fibre to enhance your paddle shift feedback and overall driving experience.

     

    • Carbon Side Grip Inserts

    Add side grip inserts for extra comfort and style. These can be customized in different carbon fibre choices and finishing to match your preferences and improve your grip.

     

    • Button Frame

    Customize the button frame to match your steering wheel's design. Choose from different carbon fibre and finishing options for a smooth integration with your steering wheel design.

     

    • Panel

    Select the perfect panel choice and finishing to complement your steering wheel. Options include (But not limited to) gloss black and various carbon fibre choices and finishing.

     

    • Horn Cover

    Finish off your custom steering wheel with a horn cover that matches your style and overall steering wheel design. Choose from (But not limited to) leather or Alcantara, stitching colours of your choice and logo emblem finishing.

    LED Functions

    Elevate your driving experience with our LED steering wheel. The LED module connects directly to your car's OBD system, delivering real-time information of your vehicle - ensuring you hit the perfect shift every time with instant feedback and seamless integration.

     

    LED display provides real-time information such as RPM/speed, engine/turbo load, engine temperature, battery voltage, 0-100 timer, etc.

     

    • Improved Driving Performance
    LED race shifting lights provide real-time feedback on your engine's RPM, allowing you to time your gear shifts perfectly. This can lead to smoother transitions and optimal performance.

     

    • Enhanced Safety
    By having LED indicators right on your steering wheel, you can keep your eyes on the road instead of glancing at the dashboard. This reduces distractions and enhances overall driving safety, particularly during intense driving conditions.

     

    • Quick Reaction Time
    LED shifting lights help you react faster by providing immediate visual cues. This is particularly beneficial in racing or spirited driving, where split-second decisions can make a significant difference.

     

    • Modern Aesthetic
    LED race shifting lights add a modern, high-tech look to your steering wheel. This feature not only enhances functionality but also gives your vehicle a more sophisticated and sporty appearance.

     

    • Customizable Alerts
    Many LED systems allow customization of the light patterns and colors, letting you set up alerts that suit your driving style and preferences. This personalized touch can improve your driving experience and make gear shifting more intuitive.

     

    • Increased Engagement
    With LED shifting lights, driving becomes a more engaging and interactive experience. The visual feedback keeps you connected with your vehicle's performance, making each drive more enjoyable and immersive.

     

    Incorporating LED race shifting lights into your steering wheel combines advanced technology with practical benefits, enhancing both your driving performance and the overall driving experience. Experience the future of driving with LED race shifting lights.
